Content:
convert a string to SCREAMING_SNAKE_CASE
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
>  "NuShell" | str screaming-snake-case
NU_SHELL

```
convert a string to SCREAMING_SNAKE_CASE
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
>  "this_is_the_second_case" | str screaming-snake-case
THIS_IS_THE_SECOND_CASE

```
